  "2236490": {
    "name": "Lost Abroad Café: A Language Learning Management Sim",
    "steam_appid": 2236490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "选一个国家开咖啡店，在发展您的业务的同时学习那国的语言！你可以在洛杉矶、墨西哥城、巴黎、米兰、柏林、上海、首尔和京都开店，学习英语、西班牙语、法语、意大利语、德语、中文（普通话）、韩语和日语！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/96936c3ee247b53aab132d2c15d4dc43.poster.avif?t=1752277140\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/96936c3ee247b53aab132d2c15d4dc43.webm?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/96936c3ee247b53aab132d2c15d4dc43.mp4?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在接待顾客的时候，您将在沉浸式环境中学到最地道的日常用语。你可以点击任何单词显示其含义，并可以随时开关订单的声音和文字，自由定义你想要的学习体验。和那些充斥于语言学习软件和课堂中的没用的无聊短语说拜拜！有了 Lost Abroad Café，你将能够在旅行中轻松地在咖啡店点单，体验当母语者的乐趣！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/e60b3a091d929b4f391be856bf4c4cd3.poster.avif?t=1752277140\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/e60b3a091d929b4f391be856bf4c4cd3.webm?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/e60b3a091d929b4f391be856bf4c4cd3.mp4?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>去一个国家学习她的语言是最好的语言学习方式，因为每当你在日常生活中使用语言时，你会得到即时反馈。但并非每个人都有随时去一个国家生活的机会。但现在，有了 Lost Abroad Café，你可以在自家客厅或者上班的地铁里获得地道的语言环境和即时反馈，体验在别国旅居的快乐！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/585cc8b2c25c47e744bfd5a048fb242f.poster.avif?t=1752277140\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/585cc8b2c25c47e744bfd5a048fb242f.webm?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/585cc8b2c25c47e744bfd5a048fb242f.mp4?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>随着语言技能的提升，你可以用卖咖啡和美食赚的钱来升级咖啡馆的设备和原料！新设备让你可以可以使用更多更好的原料来制作更好更高级的餐点，吸引更多的客人！而每个国家也都有自己的特产，让你在学习语言的同时也了解当地的风土人情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/405c3758f2ae0e50777ea7958e920f97.poster.avif?t=1752277140\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/405c3758f2ae0e50777ea7958e920f97.webm?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/405c3758f2ae0e50777ea7958e920f97.mp4?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果没有竞争，学语言的乐趣就会大打折扣。在排行榜里你能看到每个语言里最风云的咖啡店老板。加油，你也可以登顶排行榜，做个值得向朋友炫耀的风云掌柜！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/790bfe5c38d522335270a7bb8172a04f.poster.avif?t=1752277140\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/790bfe5c38d522335270a7bb8172a04f.webm?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236490/extras/790bfe5c38d522335270a7bb8172a04f.mp4?t=1752277140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lost Abroad Café 还在积极开发中，所以你可以加入我们的 Discord 来影响游戏的未来！在 Discord 上和其他学习者互动，并直接向我们提供游戏的反馈和你想要的游戏方式和内容。现在就加入我们的语言学习者社区，无尽可能的语言世界在等你！",
